## Python with Line Numbers

```python ['lines:1,3-5']
def greet(name):
    message = f"Hello, {name}!"
    print(message)
    print("Welcome to SlideDeckML!")
    return message

greet("World")
```

Lines 1, 3-5 are highlighted!

