## TypeScript with Custom Line Start

```typescript ['start:42']
interface Presentation {
    title: string;
    author: string;
    slides: Slide[];
}

class SlideDeck implements Presentation {
    constructor(
        public title: string,
        public author: string,
        public slides: Slide[]
    ) {}
}
```

Line numbering starts at 42!

